<font face="sans-serif" size="71">took me to a good friend of his,
who performed an abortion.</font>

341
00:33:53,720 --> 00:33:57,556
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We were both relieved.
We didn't want children.</font>

342
00:33:57,933 --> 00:34:00,226
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Not then, anyway.</font>

343
00:34:06,650 --> 00:34:09,068
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It doesn't make any sense.</font>

344
00:34:09,819 --> 00:34:12,321
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nothing fits together.</font>

345
00:34:13,281 --> 00:34:16,450
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And the guilty conscience
you feel over little things.</font>

346
00:34:16,576 --> 00:34:18,577
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You understand?</font>

347
00:34:18,745 --> 00:34:21,997
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And what about all the things
you'd decided to do?</font>

348
00:34:22,123 --> 00:34:24,917
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't you have
to do them anymore?</font>

349
00:34:26,586 --> 00:34:28,545
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Is it possible to be</font>

350
00:34:28,672 --> 00:34:31,674
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">one and the same person
at the very same time...</font>

351
00:34:31,800 --> 00:34:33,842
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I mean, two people?</font>

352
00:34:33,969 --> 00:34:36,136
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">God, I'm being silly!</font>

353
00:34:36,471 --> 00:34:39,765
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Anyway, there's no reason
to start blubbering.</font>

354
00:34:40,684 --> 00:34:43,102
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll get a handkerchief.</font>

355
00:35:04,582 --> 00:35:06,542
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's almost morning...</font>

356
00:35:07,544 --> 00:35:09,920
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and it's still raining.</font>

357
00:35:16,636 --> 00:35:19,263
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've been talking nonstop</font>

358
00:35:19,389 --> 00:35:21,473
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">while you've just listened.</font>

359
00:35:21,599 --> 00:35:23,392
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How boring for you.</font>

360
00:35:23,518 --> 00:35:26,520
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What could possibly
interest you about my life?</font>

361
00:35:27,188 --> 00:35:29,481
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">People should be like you.</font>

362
00:35:30,942 --> 00:35:33,027
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You know what I thought</font>

363
00:35:33,153 --> 00:35:35,821
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">after I saw a film
of yours one night?</font>

364
00:35:35,989 --> 00:35:38,824
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">When I got home and looked
in the mirror, I thought,</font>

365
00:35:38,950 --> 00:35:40,951
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"We look alike."</font>

366
00:35:41,953 --> 00:35:44,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't get me wrong.
You're much more beautiful.</font>

367
00:35:44,497 --> 00:35:46,498
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But we're alike somehow.</font>

368
00:35:46,666 --> 00:35:50,919
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think I could turn into you
if I really tried.</font>

369
00:35:51,338 --> 00:35:53,339
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I mean inside.</font>

370
00:35:55,175 --> 00:35:58,344
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You could be me
just like that...</font>

371
00:35:59,637 --> 00:36:02,097
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">though your soul
would be far too big.</font>

372
00:36:02,223 --> 00:36:04,683
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It would stick out
everywhere!</font>

373
00:36:08,146 --> 00:36:10,189
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Go to bed...</font>

374
00:36:10,315 --> 00:36:13,025
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">or you'll fall asleep
here at the table.</font>

375
00:36:26,539 --> 00:36:29,083
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I must go to bed now</font>

376
00:36:29,334 --> 00:36:31,543
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">or I'll fall asleep
at the table,</font>

377
00:36:31,711 --> 00:36:34,088
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and that would be
rather uncomfortable.</font>

378
00:36:37,884 --> 00:36:39,385
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Good night.</font>

379
00:39:39,857 --> 00:39:41,567
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Elisabet...</font>

380
00:39:44,279 --> 00:39:46,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">did you speak to me
last night?</font>

381
00:40:18,187 --> 00:40:20,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Were you
in my room last night?</font>

382
00:41:03,358 --> 00:41:05,692
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Shall I take your mail too?</font>

383
00:41:07,028 --> 00:41:08,904
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let me have a taste.</font>

384
00:41:10,823 --> 00:41:12,282
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">See ya.</font>

385
00:42:19,142 --> 00:42:22,102
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"Dear friend,
I could live like this forever.</font>

386
00:42:22,228 --> 00:42:25,188
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The silence, the seclusion,
reducing my needs,</font>

387
00:42:25,314 --> 00:42:29,234
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">feeling my battered soul finally
start to straighten itself out.</font>

388
00:42:34,574 --> 00:42:37,909
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Alma pampers me
in the most touching way.</font>

389
00:42:39,954 --> 00:42:43,915
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think she's actually enjoying it here
and that she's very fond of me,</font>

390
00:42:44,041 --> 00:42:48,003
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">perhaps even a bit smitten
in a charming, subconscious way.</font>

391
00:42:48,129 --> 00:42:51,757
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">In any case,
it's a lot of fun studying her.</font>

392
00:43:01,017 --> 00:43:04,019
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sometimes she cries
over past sins...</font>

393
00:43:04,145 --> 00:43:07,230
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">an orgy with a strange boy
and a subsequent abortion.</font>

394
00:43:07,356 --> 00:43:10,150
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She complains
that her notions about life</font>

395
00:43:10,276 --> 00:43:13,028
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">fail to accord with her actions."</font>

396
00:48:57,456 --> 00:48:59,624
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see
you're reading a play.</font>

397
00:49:00,084 --> 00:49:03,419
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's a healthy sign.
I'll tell the doctor.</font>

398
00:49:06,757 --> 00:49:08,842
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You think we should
leave here soon?</font>

399
00:49:08,968 --> 00:49:11,177
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm starting
to miss the city.</font>

400
00:49:11,679 --> 00:49:13,388
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Aren't you?</font>

401
00:49:29,071 --> 00:49:32,115
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Would you like
to make me really happy?</font>

402
00:49:33,325 --> 00:49:36,995
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know it's asking a lot,
but I could use your help right now.</font>

403
00:49:37,538 --> 00:49:39,122
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nothing dangerous.</font>

404
00:49:39,248 --> 00:49:42,000
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I do wish
you'd talk to me.</font>

405
00:49:42,126 --> 00:49:44,335
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Doesn't have to be
anything special.</font>

406
00:49:44,503 --> 00:49:48,006
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We could talk about anything...
what to have for dinner,</font>

407
00:49:48,132 --> 00:49:50,758
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">whether the water's
cold now after the storm,</font>

408
00:49:50,885 --> 00:49:53,344
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">whether it's too cold
to go swimming.</font>

409
00:49:53,512 --> 00:49:56,598
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Just talk for a few minutes.
One minute.</font>

410
00:49:56,724 --> 00:49:59,017
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You could read to me
from your book.</font>

411
00:49:59,185 --> 00:50:00,602
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Just say a few words.</font>

412
00:50:03,564 --> 00:50:05,690
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I have to try
not to get angry.</font>

413
00:50:05,858 --> 00:50:07,984
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's your business
if you want to keep quiet.</font>

414
00:50:08,110 --> 00:50:11,112
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I need you
to talk to me now.</font>

415
00:50:13,741 --> 00:50:15,575
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Can't you just say</font>

416
00:50:15,701 --> 00:50:17,243
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">one word?</font>

417
00:50:19,872 --> 00:50:21,956
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I knew you'd refuse.</font>

418
00:50:23,167 --> 00:50:25,376
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You can't know how I feel.</font>

419
00:50:27,004 --> 00:50:29,380
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I always thought great artists</font>

420
00:50:29,548 --> 00:50:32,467
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">felt this great compassion
for other people...</font>

421
00:50:33,177 --> 00:50:35,929
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">that they created
out of great compassion</font>

422
00:50:36,055 --> 00:50:38,056
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and a need to help.</font>

423
00:50:38,224 --> 00:50:40,225
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That was silly of me.</font>

424
00:50:43,896 --> 00:50:46,773
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You've used me.
For what, I don't know.</font>

425
00:50:46,899 --> 00:50:50,401
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Now that you don't need me
anymore, you toss me aside.</font>

426
00:50:50,527 --> 00:50:54,239
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes, I hear perfectly well
how phony that sounds!</font>

427
00:50:54,365 --> 00:50:56,824
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"You've used me, and now
you're tossing me aside."</font>

428
00:50:56,951 --> 00:51:00,078
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But it's true... every word.
And these glasses!</font>

429
00:51:09,088 --> 00:51:11,089
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You've hurt me badly.</font>

430
00:51:11,882 --> 00:51:14,550
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You've been laughing at me
behind my back.</font>

431
00:51:16,428 --> 00:51:18,888
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I read the letter
you wrote to the doctor.</font>

432
00:51:19,014 --> 00:51:23,101
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It wasn't sealed,
and I read the whole thing.</font>

433
00:51:25,062 --> 00:51:27,313
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You got me to talk,</font>

434
00:51:27,439 --> 00:51:29,774
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">to tell you things
I've never told anyone.</font>

435
00:51:29,900 --> 00:51:33,027
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then you go and pass it on.
Great study material, eh?</font>

436
00:51:33,153 --> 00:51:34,737
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're not...</font>

437
00:51:34,989 --> 00:51:36,990
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're going to talk now!</font>

438
00:51:37,116 --> 00:51:40,368
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you have something
to say, by God...</font>

439
00:51:53,632 --> 00:51:55,300
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, don't!</font>

440
00:52:07,187 --> 00:52:09,647
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Scared there for a minute,
weren't you?</font>

441
00:52:11,483 --> 00:52:15,361
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">For a second you were
genuinely scared, weren't you?</font>

442
00:52:15,946 --> 00:52:18,489
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">A genuine
fear of death, huh?</font>

443
00:52:19,074 --> 00:52:21,659
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"Alma's gone crazy,"
you thought.</font>

444
00:52:21,827 --> 00:52:24,412
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Just what kind of person
are you anyway?</font>

445
00:52:25,289 --> 00:52:28,875
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Or maybe you just thought,
"I'll remember that face,</font>

446
00:52:29,001 --> 00:52:31,711
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">that tone of voice,
that expression."</font>

447
00:52:31,837 --> 00:52:34,339
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll give you something
you won't forget!</font>

448
00:52:56,195 --> 00:52:58,029
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're laughing, are you?</font>

449
00:52:59,782 --> 00:53:02,200
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Things aren't
that simple for me.</font>

450
00:53:02,743 --> 00:53:04,702
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Or so funny either.</font>

451
00:53:05,788 --> 00:53:08,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But you always have
your laugh.</font>

452
00:54:33,375 --> 00:54:35,626
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Does it have
to be like this?</font>

453
00:54:38,380 --> 00:54:42,508
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Is it really so important
not to lie, to tell the truth,</font>

454
00:54:42,634 --> 00:54:44,969
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">to speak in a genuine
tone of voice?</font>

455
00:54:45,971 --> 00:54:49,307
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Can a person really live
without babbling away,</font>

456
00:54:49,475 --> 00:54:53,519
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">without lying and making up
excuses and evading things?</font>

457
00:54:54,813 --> 00:54:57,398
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Isn't it better
to just let yourself</font>

458
00:54:57,524 --> 00:55:00,359
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">be silly and sloppy
and dishonest?</font>

459
00:55:02,112 --> 00:55:06,324
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Maybe a person gets better by just
letting herself be who she is.</font>

460
00:55:10,162 --> 00:55:12,163
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, you don't understand.</font>

461
00:55:13,248 --> 00:55:14,999
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You don't understand
what I'm saying.</font>

462
00:55:15,167 --> 00:55:17,210
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's no reaching
someone like you.</font>

463
00:55:17,336 --> 00:55:19,295
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The doctor said
you're mentally healthy,</font>

464
00:55:19,421 --> 00:55:21,506
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but I wonder if your madness
isn't the worst kind.</font>

465
00:55:21,673 --> 00:55:23,341
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You act healthy,</font>

466
00:55:23,509 --> 00:55:26,010
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and the worst thing is,
everyone believes you.</font>

467
00:55:26,136 --> 00:55:29,347
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Except me, because
I know how rotten you are.</font>

468
00:55:35,729 --> 00:55:37,522
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">God, what am I doing?</font>

469
00:55:41,026 --> 00:55:43,152
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Elisabet, forgive me.</font>

470
00:55:43,278 --> 00:55:45,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm behaving like an idiot.</font>

471
00:55:45,364 --> 00:55:48,991
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't know what got into me.
I'm here to help you.</font>

472
00:55:49,117 --> 00:55:51,702
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It was that awful letter.</font>

473
00:55:51,912 --> 00:55:53,871
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I was so disappointed.</font>

474
00:55:54,039 --> 00:55:57,458
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You asked me
to talk about myself.</font>

475
00:55:58,043 --> 00:56:00,670
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It felt so good. You seemed
so kind and understanding.</font>

476
00:56:00,796 --> 00:56:02,880
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'd had a lot to drink,</font>

477
00:56:03,048 --> 00:56:05,508
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and it felt so good
to talk about it all.</font>

478
00:56:05,634 --> 00:56:07,969
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And I suppose
I was flattered</font>

479
00:56:08,095 --> 00:56:11,556
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">that a great actress like you
would bother to listen.</font>

480
00:56:11,723 --> 00:56:14,308
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I even thought
it would be nice if what I said</font>

481
00:56:14,434 --> 00:56:16,727
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">were of some use to you.</font>

482
00:56:17,229 --> 00:56:20,731
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But that's awful, isn't it?
Sheer exhibitionism.</font>

483
00:56:20,899 --> 00:56:23,901
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Elisabet,
I want you to forgive me.</font>

484
00:56:24,069 --> 00:56:27,280
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I like you so much.
You mean so much to me.</font>

485
00:56:27,406 --> 00:56:29,323
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've learned
so much from you.</font>

486
00:56:29,449 --> 00:56:31,325
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let's not part as enemies.</font>

487
00:56:54,433 --> 00:56:58,269
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You won't forgive me
because you're too proud!</font>

488
00:56:58,395 --> 00:57:02,273
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You won't stoop to my level
because you don't have to!</font>

489
00:57:02,441 --> 00:57:05,443
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I won't...</font>

490
01:01:11,481 --> 01:01:13,524
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">...we don't speak...</font>

491
01:01:13,692 --> 01:01:14,900
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">...don't listen...</font>

492
01:01:15,026 --> 01:01:16,735
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">...can't understand...</font>

493
01:01:21,491 --> 01:01:23,158
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">...what means...</font>

494
01:01:23,285 --> 01:01:25,661
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">...to persuade... to listen...</font>

495
01:02:09,164 --> 01:02:11,999
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">When you sleep,
your face goes slack...</font>

496
01:02:14,878 --> 01:02:17,546
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and your mouth
is swollen and ugly.</font>

497
01:02:20,592 --> 01:02:23,260
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's a nasty wrinkle
on your forehead.</font>

498
01:02:31,519 --> 01:02:34,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You smell
of sleep and tears...</font>

499
01:02:38,276 --> 01:02:41,028
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and I can see
the pulse in your neck.</font>

500
01:02:42,280 --> 01:02:45,324
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's a scar there
that you cover with makeup.</font>

501
01:02:51,456 --> 01:02:53,499
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's calling again.</font>

502
01:02:55,043 --> 01:02:57,544
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll find out
what he wants from us...</font>

503
01:02:58,546 --> 01:03:01,548
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">far away out here
in our solitude.</font>

504
01:03:28,702 --> 01:03:30,828
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry if I frightened you.</font>

505
01:03:32,080 --> 01:03:33,914
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm not Elisabet.</font>

506
01:03:34,290 --> 01:03:36,709
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm not here
to make demands.</font>

507
01:03:37,168 --> 01:03:39,294
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I didn't mean to disturb you.</font>

508
01:03:39,504 --> 01:03:41,588
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You think
I don't understand?</font>

509
01:03:41,715 --> 01:03:44,508
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The doctor
explained everything.</font>

510
01:03:45,844 --> 01:03:49,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But the hardest part
is explaining to your little boy.</font>

511
01:03:49,764 --> 01:03:51,807
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I do the best I can.</font>

512
